snippet.title: Leah Janae
snippet.description:
My name is Leah,
I am 29 years old and Youtube is my passion!
On my channel you will find all of my crazy obsessions...anything from Makeup, TJ Maxx Finds, Candles, Hygiene, & Fashion!
I'm a huge shopper as well. You will find all sorts of hauls from Sephora, Ulta, TJ Maxx, and Bath & Body Works going over their new products.
There is something for everyone on my channel and I hope you will Subscribe to see more :)

** If you are a company who would like to partner with me on a sponsored video please email mackenzie@1am.management
